                     <span style="font-size:26px;">

                        Self-Catering Accommodation in Bloubergstrand

                 <div class="txtNew" data-min-height="933" data-packed="false" id="comp-j4rid6z3" style="top:121px;bottom:;left:0;right:;width:980px;height:auto;position:absolute;min-height:933px;margin-left:calc((100% - 980px) * 0.5)">
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                   <span style="font-family:comic sans ms,comic-sans-w01-regular,comic-sans-w02-regular,comic-sans-w10-regular,cursive;">
                    <span style="font-size:20px;">
                     <span style="color:#000000;">
                      Are you searching for well appointed, plush, self-catering accommodation in Blouberg? Accommodation that is right on the beach and that offers unbroken sea views, as well as views of Robben Island and Table Mountain. Our Blouberg accommodation portfolio includes 1, 2 and 3 bedroom self-catering apartments that are ideal for both business travellers and holidaymakers alike. We guarantee an enjoyable stay in one of our modern and convenient accommodation suites located on the beachfront. Book online today!
                     </span>
                    </span>
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                   <span style="font-family:comic sans ms,comic-sans-w01-regular,comic-sans-w02-regular,comic-sans-w10-regular,cursive;">
                    <span style="font-size:20px;">
                     <span style="color:#000000;">
                      Our Blouberg self-catering accommodation is situated along central Marine Drive, with easy access to the main highways. This is convenience at its best being located a stone’s throw away from the soft sandy beaches, and within walking distance of a variety of tantalising restaurants and exciting activities.
                     </span>
                    </span>
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                   <span style="font-family:comic sans ms,comic-sans-w01-regular,comic-sans-w02-regular,comic-sans-w10-regular,cursive;">
                    <span style="font-size:20px;">
                     <span style="color:#000000;">
                      Our self-catering accommodation offers all the facilities and mod cons expected from top rated accommodation establishments, however at a fraction of the cost.  Guests enjoy a secure parking bay with control access. There is a heated swimming pool, which is the perfect spot to relax and soak up Cape Town's sun, or even for an after dinner swim. There are BBQ facilities at the swimming pool.
                     </span>
                    </span>
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                   <span style="font-family:comic sans ms,comic-sans-w01-regular,comic-sans-w02-regular,comic-sans-w10-regular,cursive;">
                    <span style="font-size:20px;">
                     <span style="color:#000000;">
                      Our Blouberg self-catering accommodation provides the ultimate in comfort and homeliness. All units offer a flat screen TV and DSTV with selected channels. Each apartment has a fully equipped kitchen, a spacious lounge area with comfortable furnishing and a balcony or terrace. Internet can be arranged if required. Units are serviced from Monday to Friday and linen is changed every five days, or as often as you need for a small extra fee.
                     </span>
                    </span>
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                   <span style="font-family:comic sans ms,comic-sans-w01-regular,comic-sans-w02-regular,comic-sans-w10-regular,cursive;">
                    <span style="font-size:20px;">
                     <span style="color:#000000;">
                      Blouberg is a prime tourist destination for leisure, the business traveller and water sports fans. If time permits be sure to experience some of the best boogie boarding, kite surfing and wind surfing the area has to offer, which is all accessible right from your doorstep.
                     </span>
                    </span>
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                  </p>
                  <p class="font_8" style="font-size:20px;">
                   <span style="font-family:comic sans ms,comic-sans-w01-regular,comic-sans-w02-regular,comic-sans-w10-regular,cursive;">
                    <span style="font-size:20px;">
                     <span style="color:#000000;">
                      At Blouberg Beachfront Accommodation we pride ourselves on offering an exceptional service to our guests. When frequenting a self-catering apartment in our portfolio you will be highly regarded and well hosted. Book online today!
                     </span>
                    </span>
                   </span>
                  </p>
